    "content": "Song:           'According To You'\r\nArtist:         Orianthi\r\nAlbum:          Believe (Geffen)\r\nTabbed By:      JeffDiablo (lowestfrequency@yahoo.com)\r\nTuning:         5-string: standard (BEADG low-to-high)\r\n\r\nPerformance Notes\r\nI tap the intro and you could do the same for the middle interlude but I find playing \r\nlower F, C, and D to be more efficient.\r\n\r\nNotes with '.' over them are played staccato.  Ending seems to be in free time.\r\n\r\n\r\n[tab]Intro\r\nG|17~--------------|-----------------|\r\nD|-----------------|17~--------------|\r\nA|8~---------------|-----------------|\r\nE|-----------------|8~---------------|\r\nB|-----------------|-----------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]VERSE 1 [bass tacit 8 measures]\r\nG|----------------|----------------|----------------|----------------|\r\nD|----------------|----------------|----------------|----------------|\r\nA|----------------|3---3---3-3-3-3-|5---5---5-5-5-5-|1---1---1-1-1-1-|\r\nE|1---1---1-1-1-1-|----------------|----------------|----------------|\r\nB|----------------|----------------|----------------|----------------|[/tab]\r\n[tab]                                                         .\r\nG|----------------|----------------|----------------|----------------|\r\nD|----------------|----------------|----------------|----------------|\r\nA|----------------|3-3-3-3-3-3-3~--|5-5-5-5-5-5-5~--|1-1-1-----------|\r\nE|1-1-1-1-1-1-1~--|----------------|----------------|----------------|\r\nB|----------------|----------------|----------------|----------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]CHORUS 1\r\nG|----------------|----------------|----------------|----------------|\r\nD|----------------|----------------|----------------|----------------|\r\nA|1-1-1-1-1-1-1-1-|3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3-|----------------|----------------|\r\nE|----------------|----------------|----------------|3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3-|\r\nB|----------------|----------------|3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3-|----------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|------------